.PP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
.RS 4
Display help message n' exit\&.
.RE
.PP
\fB\-q\fR, \fB\-\-quiet\fR
.RS 4
Report errors only\&. Da warnings which do not require any action from tha user won\*(Aqt be displayed\&.
.RE
.PP
\fB\-r\fR, \fB\-\-read\-only\fR
.RS 4
Execute the
\fBpwck\fR
