.RE
.PP
\fB\-s\fR, \fB\-\-sort\fR
.RS 4
Sort entries in
/etc/passwd
and
/etc/shadow
by UID\&.
.RE
.PP
By default,
\fBpwck\fR
operates on tha files
/etc/passwd
and
/etc/shadow\&. Da user may select alternate filez wit the
\fIpasswd\fR
and
\fIshadow\fR
